README for hmemo/test
=====================

Executable: hmemoTest

Note: Context that should be tested has to be specified

Run it:

    hmemoTest --SCAI_CONTEXT=Host                  !! run it on Host
    hmemoTest --SCAI_CONTEXT=CUDA                  !! run it on CUDA, default device
    hmemoTest --SCAI_CONTEXT=CUDA --SCAI_DEVICE=1  !! run it on CUDA, further device

The following functionalities are tested:

 - MemoryTest  -> Test device and host memory of the context
 - HArrayTest  -> Tests HArray operations with focus on the test context
 - ContextTest -> Tests operations on context

